lhk / listhook                Lists hooks
 
   Format:
      ;lhk
               Lists all hooks belonging to current profiles
      ;lhk -w
               Lists all hooks associated with the current world 
      ;lhk -g
               Lists all hooks associated with the current guild
      ;lhk -r
               Lists all hooks associated with the current race
      ;lhk -c
               Lists all hooks associated with the current character
      ;lhk -x <category>
               Lists all hooks belonging to the current custom profile derived
                  from the category (template) <category>
      ;lhk -d <prof>
               Lists all hooks belonging to the profile <prof>
      ;lhk -i
               Lists all active hook interfaces
 
   User commands:
      lhk / listhk / listhook
